br.com.lett.crawlernode.crawlers.brasil

Class BrasilUnicaarcondicionadoCrawler

  • java.lang.Object
    • br.com.lett.crawlernode.kernel.Crawler
      • br.com.lett.crawlernode.crawlers.brasil.BrasilUnicaarcondicionadoCrawler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Runnable

    public class BrasilUnicaarcondicionadoCrawler
extends Crawler
    Crawling notes (20/07/2016): 1) For this crawler, we have one url per each sku. There is no page is more than one sku in it. 2) There is no stock information for skus in this ecommerce by the time this crawler was made. 3) There is no marketplace in this ecommerce by the time this crawler was made. 4) The sku page identification is done simply looking the html element. 5) Even if a product is unavailable, its price is displayed. 6) There is no internalPid for skus in this ecommerce. The internalPid must be a number that is the same for all the variations of a given sku. 7) There is no categories in product page in this market. Examples: ex1 (available): http://www.unicaarcondicionado.com.br/ar-condicionado-split-hi-wall-carrier-x-power-inverter-9000-btus-frio-220v.html ex2 (unavailable): http://www.unicaarcondicionado.com.br/ar-condicionado-split-hi-wall-elgin-compact-9000-btus-frio-110v.html Optimizations notes: No optimizations.
